gobblin.runtime.api

Interface MutableJobCatalog

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JobCatalog, JobCatalogListenersContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FSJobCatalog, InMemoryJobCatalog, MutableCachingJobCatalog

    @Alpha
public interface MutableJobCatalog
extends JobCatalog
    A JobCatalog that can have its Collection of JobSpecs modified programmatically. Note that jobs in a job catalog can change from the outside. This is covered by the base JobCatalog interface.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

    • Method Detail

      • put

        void put(JobSpec jobSpec)
        Registers a new JobSpec. If a JobSpec with the same JobSpec.getUri() exists, it will be replaced.

      • remove

        void remove(URI uri)
        Removes an existing JobSpec with the given URI. A no-op if such JobSpec does not exist.
